00:00:01,413 --> 00:00:03,154
In these next few episodes, we want to

3
00:00:03,154 --> 00:00:05,878
tour through the remarkable personality

4
00:00:05,878 --> 00:00:08,776
and unique character of
the prophet Muhammad,

5
00:00:08,776 --> 00:00:10,472
peace and blessings be upon him,

6
00:00:10,472 --> 00:00:12,726
as one of the strongest cases

7
00:00:12,726 --> 00:00:14,370
in support of his prophethood.

8
00:00:14,370 --> 00:00:16,392
And we have to begin with honesty.

9
00:00:16,392 --> 00:00:17,785
Because the prophet Muhammad,

10
00:00:17,785 --> 00:00:19,362
peace and blessings be upon him,

11
00:00:19,362 --> 00:00:22,460
was not just a man whose
honesty and integrity

12
00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:24,560
were well-known among his people.

13
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:26,602
This was a man who was literally,

14
00:00:26,602 --> 00:00:30,634
officially, nicknamed El
Amin, The Trustworthy.

15
00:00:30,634 --> 00:00:33,385
(air whooshes)
(choir vocalizes)

16
